data.description: Adorable bungalow loaded with charm and character! Open the door to a living room featuring a woodburning fireplace, hardwood floors and then move onto the formal dining room and cute kitchen fully loaded with appliances! 2 nice sized bedrooms and a cute bath complete the main floor. Full basement with rec room (treadmill stays!) HWH new in 2023 and then open the back door to a large patio and super sized fenced shady yard! It's amazing! Shed stays for storing the lawn mowers the seller is conveying! Relax on the composite front porch swing and call this gem home sweet home!
